comments.body:
Do you want to move the "low-level" testing methods into a nested object?
Something like:
```
class ParticipantTestContext {
  object lowLevel {
    // low-level methods here
  }
```
This way it is fairly obvious that these are discouraged from general purpose use. What do you think?
